# dot-np-directory check: JSON output contains the error in the errors array
# and exits 2. warnings is always present as an empty array.

! exec np admin doctor --json
np-json-array-len errors 1
np-json-array-len warnings 0
stdout '"dot-np-directory"'
stdout 'no .np/ directory found'

-- CLAUDE.md --
Use np to manage issues. Run `np agent prime` for setup.
